The Kenya Urban Roads Authority has warned of massive traffic on Sunday ahead of the grand Nairobi Bike race. In a notice on Monday, Kura said traffic along Lang'ata Road Aerodrome road , lower hill road, Uhuru Highway, Haile Selassie avenue and Bunyala Road will be affected. "This is due to the race happening on Sunday, December 1, from 8 am till 12. 30 pm. Motorists are advised to use alternative routes," read the notice.